                "name": "Aleks Stefanovska",
                "href": "/profile/Aleks-Stefanovska"
            },
            "answer_text": "To help you best, I\u2019d recommend you edit the question and give more information. In general, and almost 99%, the answer would be YES! The 1% is if you write an essay about something inappropriate, unsavory, or illegal (writing an essay in those categories may be a call for support and help, and every person should have access to help). So the questions I have for you are: (1) what do you mean by weird? and (2) why do you want to write about it? Again, if you update the question with those two answers, more people can give you specific guidance. Lastly - what may be weird to one person, is normal to another. So, 99% of the time, I wouldn\u2019t worry. Good luck, Aleks ",
